headline.print_headline: Beckham's Miami Stadium Plan Hits Stormy Waters
headline.main: Beckham's Miami Stadium Plan Hits Stormy Waters

lead_paragraph: David Beckham's dream of building a futuristic waterfront  stadium in Miami that would house his own professional soccer team has turned into a "not in my backyard" clash, pitting the retired English superstar against one of the world's top cruise lines.
